            "value": "<p><strong>Usage</strong> imbued in one or two weapon ikons that both have the thrown trait (see text)</p><hr /><p>Your ikons bond like a pair of one-winged birds. This feat can be imbued in either a single ikon with multiple copies, such as one produced by the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.classfeatures.Item.Shadow Sheath] or with the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Twin Stars] feat, or two separate ikons (bypassing the normal limit per ikon feat).</p>\n<p><strong>Immanence</strong> As long as you hold one ikon, the other will return to find its partner. Both ikons gain the returning rune.</p>\n<p><strong>Transcendenceâ€”</strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Rejoin in Flight] <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> (transcendence)</p>\n<p>@Embed[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.I08t3hnpMZSRX5Ug inline]</p>"
